Addison Richards https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Addison_Richards 0 Addison Whittaker Richards, Jr. (October 20, 1902 – March 22, 1964) was an American actor of film and television. Richards appeared in more than three hundred films between 1933 and his death. Addison_Whittaker_Richards , Jr. ( October_20_,_1902 – March_22_,_1964 ) was an_American_actor of film_and_television .
